level.heading: Legislative History of Laws
level.text: For legislative history of D.C. Law 10-236, see Historical and Statutory Notes following § 2-1207.02.

level.heading: Miscellaneous Notes

Revision of subchapter: D.C. Law 12-26 revised this subchapter by renumbering former §§ 1-2271 through 1-2291 as §§ 1-2272 through 1-2292 [§§ 2-1215.02 through 2-1215.22, 2001 Ed.], and by adding § 1-2271 [§ 2-1215.01, 2001 Ed.].
